just_use presence.go

# label: CLEAN_INFRA
# role: supports feature — online-user tracking (in-memory last_seen)

Cat POSTs every 60s; a user is online if seen within OfflineThreshold
(2 minutes). Pure in-memory — no DB, no persistence. Restart = everyone
offline until the next heartbeat, which is fine because presence is an
ephemeral signal by design.
